name: Brandish Maiden Shizuku
desc:
1 non-WATER "Brandish Maiden" monster
Monsters your opponent controls lose 100 ATK/DEF for each Spell in your GY. Once per turn, during the End Phase, if this card was Special Summoned this turn: You can add 1 "Brandish" Spell from your Deck to your hand with a different name from every card in your GY. You can only Special Summon "Brandish Maiden Shizuku(s)" once per turn.
